attributes.description: Overview of Agent logs from Airlock Digital

params.markdown:
### Airlock Digital

#### Overview

This dashboard provides comprehensive visibility into agent activity within the Airlock Digital platform using the Agent log data stream.

It displays the total number of agents, highlights top hostnames and usernames to identify the most active systems and users, and categorizes agents by operating system and group. 

Policy insights are presented through a breakdown of the top 10 policies by group ID and configuration trust status. Additionally, it provides details on agent commands, and other relevant agent attributes enabling administrators to monitor deployment health, configuration consistency, and network posture effectively.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/airlock_digital/overview)**
